              >Comprehensive but more complex</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Seamless with QuickBooks</td
            >
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Key Features</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Payroll, benefits, HR tools</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Payroll, compliance, HR services</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Payroll, benefits, 401(k), HR</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Payroll, tax filing, time tracking</td
            >
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Accounting Integration</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Integrates with QuickBooks, Xero</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Integrates with QuickBooks, Xero</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Integrates with QuickBooks, Xero</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Native QuickBooks integration</td
            >
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2">Best For</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
              >Small to mid-sized businesses</td
            >
            <td class="border border-gray-600 px-4 py-2"
